        "P3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。时间轴我想用毫秒显示，从0开始。每个进程单独一个section，另外还需要一个专门的Llegadas区域来标注所有到达时刻的里程碑，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "datef",
        "axisf",
        "secti",
        "llegadas",
        "milest"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，时间格式用X，axisFormat设成%ms。Llegadas部分要放6个到达事件：P1在0时刻到达，然后P2-T1在1ms，P3-T1在2ms，P2-T2在3ms，P3-T2在4ms，P3-T3在5ms。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1_arrive",
        "P2-T1_arrive",
        "P3-T1_arrive",
        "P2-T2_arrive",
        "P3-T2_arrive",
        "P3-T3_arrive"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Llegadas区域的6个里程碑建好，都是零宽度的点事件。现在来看P1部分，它只有一个线程T1吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "arr1",
        "arr2",
        "arr3",
        "arr4",
        "arr5",
        "arr6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "P1在PaymentGateway里，T1的执行段从0到4ms，标记为active状态。然后有个I/O阻塞，6到9ms，这个要标crit，因为涉及外部调用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1-T1_exec",
        "P1-T1_IO",
        "p1t1a",
        "p1t1io"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "P1画好了，T1执行是active绿色条，I/O是crit红色条。P2也在PaymentGateway，它有两个线程T1和T2，您说下时间？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1-T1_exec",
        "P1-T1_IO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "P2-T1执行4到8ms，然后T2执行12到14ms，T2的I/O在14到16ms，也是crit。注意P2-T1到达是1ms，但执行要到4ms才开始，因为前面P1在用CPU。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P2-T1_exec",
        "P2-T2_exec",
        "P2-T2_IO",
        "p2t1a",
        "p2t2a",
        "p2t2io"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "P2完成了。现在P3在AuthVault模块，也有两个线程？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P2-T1_exec",
        "P2-T2_exec",
        "P2-T2_IO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "P3-T1执行8到12ms，active。另外P3-T2是个ULT用户级线程，8到12ms，状态标done，它和T1是并发的，共享P3的时间片。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P3-T1_exec",
        "P3-T2_ULT",
